---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Moonraker Process | Check, Build, Grow"
  description="How Moonraker works: a clear first check, a 90-day foundation build, then ongoing visibility work for qualified therapy practices."
  canonical="https://moonraker.ai/process"
  ogTitle="Moonraker Process"
  ogDescription="A clear first check, a 90-day foundation build, then ongoing visibility work."
  ogUrl="https://moonraker.ai/process"
>
<main>
  <section class="process-hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-kicker">How engagement works</div>
        <h1>A clear path forward to <span style="color: var(--color-primary)">boost your visibility.</span></h1>
        <p>Moonraker starts by checking the basics: your website, Google presence, local listings, service pages, and contact path. Then we rebuild the website foundation and close the audit gaps before moving into ongoing work.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="phase-stack" aria-label="Moonraker phases">
        <h2 class="sr-only">Our phases</h2>
        <div class="phase-preview"><div class="phase-num">0</div><div><h3>Free strategy call</h3><p>A clear review of what is working, what is missing, and whether we can help.</p></div></div>
        <div class="phase-preview"><div class="phase-num">1</div><div><h3>Foundation Rebuild</h3><p>We move the site to our Cloudflare R2 foundation, then close the visibility gaps around it.</p></div></div>
        <div class="phase-preview"><div class="phase-num">2</div><div><h3>Ongoing CORE support</h3><p>We keep improving the site, proof, reporting, video, and visibility.</p></div></div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div><div class="section-label">Timeline</div><h2>The first 90 days build the foundation first.</h2></div>
      <p>Before we ask you to commit to ongoing work, we want the website, tracking, listings, and proof system on stable ground. That makes the next phase more useful and easier to measure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <article class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-time">Phase 0</div><div><h3>Free strategy call</h3><p>We look at your website, Google profile, local listings, service pages, trust points, and booking path. You get a clear read on where things stand.</p></div></article>
      <article class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-time">Days 1-30</div><div><h3>Website foundation</h3><p>We confirm access, map priorities, and rebuild or launch the site on Moonraker's Cloudflare R2 foundation.</p></div></article>
      <article class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-time">Days 31-60</div><div><h3>Audit-driven remediation</h3><p>We improve important pages, service content, Google Business Profile, local listings, FAQs, and the proof visitors need before they contact you.</p></div></article>
      <article class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-time">Days 61-90</div><div><h3>Verification and handoff</h3><p>We organize the larger proof system, improve YouTube after access is granted, set the first reporting baseline, and document what changed.</p></div></article>
      <article class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-time">Ongoing</div><div><h3>Ongoing CORE support</h3><p>We continue improving the website, publishing proof assets, reporting progress, and recommending next steps.</p></div></article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="access-band">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="section-label">Working model</div>
      <h2>You own the accounts. We do the work inside them.</h2>
      <div class="access-grid">
        <article class="access-card"><h3>Client owns</h3><ul><li>Domain and website access</li><li>Google Business Profile</li><li>YouTube channel</li><li>Quora account or Space</li><li>Practice credentials and approvals</li></ul></article>
        <article class="access-card"><h3>Moonraker builds</h3><ul><li>Website cleanup and search basics</li><li>Clear service and location pages</li><li>Local listings and consistency</li><li>Practice proof hub</li><li>Reports and recommendations</li></ul></article>
        <article class="access-card"><h3>Outside core scope</h3><ul><li>Social media posting</li><li>Google Business Profile posts and review replies</li><li>YouTube channel creation</li><li>HIPAA, legal, or compliance consulting</li></ul></article>
      </div>
      <div class="guarantee">
        <h3>Performance Guarantee</h3>
        <p>The Performance Guarantee is only for annual plans and must be explained in the proposal or agreement. It is not a promise that every keyword will rank, and we do not present it that way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div><h2>Start with a free strategy call.</h2><p>We will look at the current foundation and show whether the 90-day foundation is the right next step.</p></div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/free-strategy-call">Book a Free Strategy Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.process-hero { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-deep) 100%); color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); padding: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 5rem) 2rem clamp(2.75rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); }
.process-hero::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 62px 62px;
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.process-hero .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hero-inner { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr .95fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem); align-items: center; }
.hero-kicker { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 800; font-size: .78rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
.process-hero h1 { color: var(--color-on-navy); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.7rem); line-height: 1.03; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
.process-hero p { color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.75; }
.phase-stack { border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); border-radius: var(--r-lg); overflow: hidden; background: var(--color-surface); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
.phase-preview { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.phase-preview:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
.phase-num { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px; display: grid; place-items: center; background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-primary); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; }
.phase-preview h3 { margin-bottom: .25rem; }
.phase-preview p { font-size: .84rem; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-muted); }
.section-wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6rem) 2rem; }
.section-label { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 800; font-size: .74rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: .7rem; }
.section-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: end; }
.section-head h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.6vw, 3rem); }
.section-head p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; }
.timeline { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
.timeline-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr; gap: 1rem; background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.25rem; }
.timeline-time { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-primary); }
.timeline-item h3 { margin-bottom: .45rem; }
.timeline-item p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.65; font-size: .92rem; }
.access-band { background: var(--color-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.access-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
.access-card { background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.35rem; }
.access-card h3 { margin-bottom: .55rem; }
.access-card ul { list-style: none; display: grid; gap: .5rem; }
.access-card li { color: var(--color-body); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.5; padding-left: 1.1rem; position: relative; }
.access-card li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: .65em; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); }
.guarantee { background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-deep) 100%); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 2rem; color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); margin-top: 2rem; }
.guarantee h3 { color: var(--color-on-navy); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
.guarantee p { color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); line-height: 1.7; }
.cta-band { position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-deep) 100%); color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); }
.cta-band::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, oklch(0.945 0.018 166 / 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 58px 58px;
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  mask-image: radial-gradient(80% 120% at 50% 0%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem) 2rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; }
.cta-inner h2 { color: var(--color-on-navy); margin-bottom: .6rem; }
.cta-inner p { color: var(--color-on-navy-dim); }
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .hero-inner, .section-head, .access-grid, .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
